{"tid":272074,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊要入西藏 買咩卡好","createTime":"2017-06-05T14:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T15:37:54.000Z","uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38fb318693062d2f0cb33f060ed3aa31966865a2","tid":272074,"uid":22855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"小弟由昆明去西藏 去7x 日左右  <br />\n應該買咩電話卡 <br />\n會唔會有d 初頭有4g 限流量 爆左就會轉無限3g 咁樣？"},{"pid":"63e21e8e37c8ab599a8f1a14165c39dc964bad4e","tid":272074,"uid":89598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟由昆明去西藏 去7x 日左右  <br />\n應該買咩電話卡 <br />\n會唔會有d 初頭有4g 限流量 爆左就會轉無限3g 咁樣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中移動十日1.5GB啦，鴨記自搵"},{"pid":"43ad6554993f38fa8fd09be2dfccc2bedeee78af","tid":272074,"uid":86929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"入藏區只可以用2G啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那政府Block曬4G/3G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申4月去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1083c81053243477f25b091224b6f15b6cb302","tid":272074,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:35:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"daa0bb46847aca2388d1602cd6fe7729f85597e1","tid":272074,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"去70幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"bf9aa78372f08ef193f29bc63985714dde945dea","tid":272074,"uid":86929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入藏區只可以用2G啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那政府Block曬4G/3G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申4月去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n純3G（即係UMTS，唔計3.5G HSPA）我都覺得頂唔順，仲要得果2G，真係text only<br />\n<br />\n如果根據返呢條維基條目：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/長期演進技術\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E6%BC%94%E9%80%B2%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93&d=Y%2BpPVQe0OTvO2ypC3%2BqKHgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=83236d6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/長期演進技術</a><br />\n<br />\nGSM係2G<br />\nGPRS係2.5G<br />\nEDGE係2.75G<br />\nUMTS係3G<br />\nHSPA係3.5G或3.75G<br />\nLTE係3.9G<br />\nLTE-A係4G</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nGSM係2G<br />\nGPRS係2.5G<br />\nEDGE係2.75G<br />\n只可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c9afb124925cce60b15d96144b2f8f2665f10a","tid":272074,"uid":48861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入藏區只可以用2G啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那政府Block曬4G/3G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申4月去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我五月去完都收到3G喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac5769f5e9d321c593801cec7045b0cc77ea881","tid":272074,"uid":86929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T11:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入藏區只可以用2G啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那政府Block曬4G/3G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申4月去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我五月去完都收到3G喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3G睇你咩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下去下藏區，冇乜旅客地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5679e95cb379fd87